"{{Short description|none}} <!-- \"none\" is preferred when the title is sufficiently descriptive; see [[WP:SDNONE]] -->\n{{EngvarB|date=November 2015}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=November 2020}}\n\n{{Politics of Myanmar}}\n\n'''[[Myanmar]]''' (formerly '''Burma''') has full diplomatic relations with 126 countries out of 192 [[Member states of the United Nations|United Nation Members States]].<ref>{{Cite web |title=Diplomatic relations established between Republic of Union of Myanmar and Republic of Guinea-Bissau {{!}} Ministry Of Information |url=https://www.moi.gov.mm/moi:eng/news/9686 |access-date=2025-08-09 |website=www.moi.gov.mm |language=en}}</ref> The country has generally maintained warmer relations with near states and is a member of the [[ASEAN|Association of Southeast Asian Nations]].<ref>{{Cite web |last=Kavi |first=Maung |date=2024-12-24 |title=Desperation Diplomacy: How Myanmar Junta Looked Abroad as It Lost Ground in 2024 |url=https://www.irrawaddy.com/opinion/analysis/myanmar-juntas-desperation-diplomacy-in-2024.html |access-date=2025-08-09 |website=The Irrawaddy |language=en-US}}</ref>\n\n== Diplomatic relations ==\nList of countries which Myanmar maintains diplomatic relations with:\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n! colspan=\"3\" |[[File:Diplomatic relations of Myanmar.svg|frameless|425x425px]]\n|-\n!\n!Country\n! Date<ref>{{Cite web |title=Diplomatic relations between Myanmar and ... |url=https://digitallibrary.un.org/search?ln=en&as=1&m1=p&p1=Diplomatic+relations+between+Myanmar+and+...&f1=series&op1=a&m2=a&p2=&f2=&op2=a&m3=a&p3=&f3=&dt=&d1d=&d1m=&d1y=&d2d=&d2m=&d2y=&rm=&ln=en&action_search=Search&sf=title&so=a&rg=50&c=United+Nations+Digital+Library+System&of=hb&fti=0&fti=0 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220513104307/https://digitallibrary.un.org/search?ln=en&as=1&m1=p&p1=Diplomatic+relations+between+Myanmar+and+...&f1=series&op1=a&m2=a&p2=&f2=&op2=a&m3=a&p3=&f3=&dt=&d1d=&d1m=&d1y=&d2d=&d2m=&d2y=&rm=&ln=en&action_search