er 2018|archive-date=14 April 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190414220704/http://sdsc.bellschool.anu.edu.au/sites/default/files/publications/attachments/2016-03/154_Burma_s_north_korean_gambit__A_challenge_to_regional_security_by_Andrew_Selth%2C_76p_0.pdf#page=17|url-status=live}}\n* Singh, N. K. (2003). ''Encyclopaedia of Bangladesh''. Anmol Publications PVT. LTD. {{ISBN|978-81-261-1390-3}}\n* Silverstein, Josef. (1980). ''Burmese politics: the dilemma of national unity''. Rutgers University Press. {{ISBN|978-0-8135-0900-6}}\n* South, Ashley. (2003). ''Mon Nationalism and Civil War in Burma: The Golden Sheldrake.'' Routledge. {{ISBN|978-0-7007-1609-8}}\n* Swanström, Niklas. ''Sino-Myanmar relations: Security and beyond'' (Institute for Security and Development Policy, 2012) [https://www.isdp.eu/content/uploads/publications/2012_swanstrom_sino-myanmar-relations.pdf online] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210822013200/https://www.isdp.eu/content/uploads/publications/2012_swanstrom_sino-myanmar-relations.pdf |date=22 August 2021 }}\n{{refend}}\n\n==External links==\n* [http://www.mofa.gov.mm/ Ministry of Foreign Affairs of Myanmar] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210421024331/http://www.mofa.gov.mm/ |date=21 April 2021 }}\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20110427223923/http://www.iss.europa.eu/nc/actualites/actualite/browse/1/article/reorienting-strategies-towards-burmamyanmar/ Reorienting strategies towards Burma/Myanmar], Opinion by Bernt Berger, May 2008, [[European Union Institute for Security Studies]]\n* [https://history.state.gov/countries/burma History of Burma – U.S. relations] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170621090822/https://history.state.gov/countries/burma |date=21 June 2017 }}\n* [http://www.thefreelibrary.com/Thai-Myanmar+relations+returning+to+normal,+Thaksin+says.-a076143572 Thai-Myanmar relations returning to normal, Thaksin says] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/2011043004203